User Story:
  ☐ Create a static app, i will give app name.
  ☐ Create a dynamic app, i will give app name.
  ☐ Rotate the secret key for my platform.
  ☐ Deploy an app, i will pass the api key, secret key. You have to sign and upload.
  ☐ List all my apps.
  ☐ If my application logs then it should be availble in logs section.

    

Non Functional Requirements:
  ☐ only one deployment at a time for a given app.
  ☐ restrict number of ongoing deployment. (caddy rate limit)
  ☐ Only one root user
  ☐ Should we keep root user and other users separate in the db?
